lead_paragraph: In the final seconds of a wild double-overtime junior college basketball game that had a combined 310 points on the scoreboard, point guard Shawn Craig still thought he would win it for United Tribes Technical College — even though he had just one other teammate on the floor.

headline.print_headline: Team Nearly Wins Basketball Game With 2 Players Left at End
